b'Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon S: Kaguya-: b"An unusual snow storm hits Tokyo and the Sailor Senshi discover that an evil snow queen Kaguya, wants to freeze the entire earth. Kakeru becomes ill and Luna wishes she could be a human to help him. \n"
